Tyrael: Personally, I think flying is a priority. It saved my life
times and again!

He looks at Blackheart as he goes in the chamber and wonders what mode
the General would take on. He was certain, though, that it would be a
terrible one.

Tyrael: I will need your help, Darkangel, but first, I have to talk to
Blackheart. If my research are succesful, we might have a worthy
addition to our troops, but the line is dangerous.
